General.Name: Ngenic AB
General.Description: Ngenic AB (publ) provides digitalized energy services for consumers, property owners, and energy companies in Sweden. It offers Ngenic Tune, a smart thermostat that collects information about weather, humidity and sunlight, and indoor and outdoor temperature, as well as helps to optimize heating system; and Ngenic Track that collects energy data. The company also provides FairShare, an individual measurement and billing for apartment buildings; Tune Highrise, a system for the control of heating systems in properties with water-based heat; Gridtuner service for load control and optimization of electricity or district heating network; and customized software and hardware solutions. The company was incorporated in 2010 and is headquartered in Uppsala, Sweden.
